===Format===
'''Battle For Revolution Season 2''' : ''July 12th - 15th
* '''Semi Finals''' : ''September 25th - 27th
** 18 teams , 3 matchdays.
** 18 matches (6 each day).
** {{bgcolortext|up|Top 8 teams}} qualify for ''Grand Finals.
* '''Grand Finals''' : ''October 2nd - 3rd
** 10 invited teams , 8 teams from Semi Finals , 2 matchdays.
** 12 matches (6 each day).

